cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.HC, cs.IR 

The paper deals with image processing and cognitive analysis of 360-degree surround photos, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also discusses the practical approach of capturing virtual reality ready content from mobile phones, which could be related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper mentions the difficulty in indexing and processing photospheres, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and graphics (cs.GR).
